reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product, just as advertised.
reviews.reviewText: Fantastic product, currently using it for my phone, Fitbit and recharging my batteries. well built and very sturdy. I would recommend it to anyone looking for a block since it has multiple inputs. I would recommend it to friends and family.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Still going strong
reviews.reviewText: These chargers work really good and last. I haven't had any problems with them and they charge fast.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I've been using these charging bricks everywhere in my house and on the go. For the price, the power output on the bricks is fantastic. There's plenty of ports on the brick to satisfy whatever I need power for at the time. Best value charging brick I've seen in a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I used this to replace a group of chargers and different cables for all of my family's devices. I just leave all the charging ports populated with various cables now, so it helped organize a bit of a mess. The charger itself seems to work well but I swear the quick charger takes longer than my Samsung charger. The downside to using this is it is heavy enough with all of the cables that it wants to fall out of the outlet. Overall happy with it and it was a value for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Little Charger Set
reviews.reviewText: These are replacing another no-name brand I got which had a lot of coil whine and a failed USB port after a few weeks. Months in and they are working great, charges fast. They have all the ports you need and if you're like me and have several devices charging at the bedside then this is perfect.
